title: HARRIS, PETERSON, AND PINKER A Conversation With Existential Comics Corey Mohler
itunes:author: Toby Buckle
itunes:summary: In this episode, I discuss the 'Intelectual Dark Web' with Existential Comic's Corey Mohler.  We cover Sam Harris, Jordan Peterson, and Steven Pinker, arguing that for supposed free thinkers, they often just seem to want to maintain the world of their youth.
